dataIdInfo.idPurp: The 2015 Inventory provides a comprehensive picture of the amount and type of developed and vacant industrial lands in the region. It contains detailed information about the quantity, utilization, status, and characteristics of the industrial lands in Metro Vancouver as of mid-2015. For more information, users are encouraged to review the 2015 ILI Summary and Technical Reports. http://www.metrovancouver.org/services/regional-planning/industrial-lands/resources/Pages/default.aspx

Consts.useLimit: "See the GVRD Data Sharing Agreement for Disclaimer and Warranties and Limitation on Liabilities with respect to the data." The data may not be copied, sold, or redistributed without the written consent of the GVRD. The data may be used in publications, reports, and the like provided that the GVRD is acknowledged as the source of the data.

dataIdInfo.idAbs: The 2015 Inventory supports Metro Vancouver 2040: Shaping our Future (Metro 2040) goals by providing information to support the protection of industrial lands, promote industrial intensification, and inform future policy development and implementation.
